<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Friendship is Magic</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
While inside Starlight Glimmer's nightmare, Princess Celestia is introduced to her hypothetical Super-Powered Evil Side: Daybreaker. Where as Princess Luna transformed into Nightmre Moon out of jealousy and bitterness towards her older sister, Daybreaker stemmed from Princess Celestia embracing her selfishness and stopped caring for anyone, potentially turning herself into a tyrannical ruler. This alone terrifies Celestia, and swears that she will never become her.	</p>
